# CODEOWNERS — populate before running scripts/bootstrap-github-settings.sh
# Without real owners, the "require code owner reviews" branch protection has no effect.
# Replace @your-org/your-team with actual GitHub users or teams.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: all files require a review
* @your-org/your-team

# Security-sensitive paths require explicit ownership
.devcontainer/ @your-org/your-team
.github/ @your-org/your-team
scripts/ @your-org/your-team
.semgrep.yml @your-org/your-team
.gitleaks.toml @your-org/your-team
SECURITY.md @your-org/your-team
CLAUDE.md @your-org/your-team
